  "name": {
    "en": "Mongolian Seventeen Potencies",
    "mn": "Арван долоон нанс"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": "The Seventeen Potencies (Арван долоон нанс - Arvan Doloon Nans) in Mongolian Traditional Medicine. These are the post-digestive qualities that determine how a substance affects the body."
  },
  "members": [
